data.text:
@emilylewisdraws When I got my skelly dress I was broke so I bought some inexpensive black tights and on Halloween morning I used acrylic paint to put bones on my legs (like yknow, leg bones).

When I finally took them off late that night I found the paint had gone through and stuck to my legs 😂
@emilylewisdraws It's been a few years for me already. I got sick of being the only one ever dressing up on campus/in my group of friends. I still have a skeleton dress tho.
